	Ms. Sterling plays Frau, a sidekick of Austin Powers' nemesis  
Dr. Evil. ``The Spy Who Shagged Me'' was scheduled to be released 
this summer. 
</P>
<P>
	Meanwhile, she will also appear as an acting coach in ``Drop  
Dead Gorgeous,'' a mock documentary about the life of beauty 
pageant contestants and their families. The New Line production was 
due out April 30. 
